title: Ep 21 - Dive Into Fear
itunes:title: Ep 21 - Dive Into Fear
description:
Some people are frozen by their fear. The thing about fear is that we always worry about something that MIGHT happen in the future, and some times something completely out of our control. In this episode we talk about fear and give the top three tips to overcome your fear to make the life of your dreams.
